-dvd-copy-software\">Mac DVD burning application</a>. The Roxio Popcorn application is a more basic version of the Toast Titanium 11 program. The interfaces of the two Mac DVD burning software programs are almost the same. However, Toast Titanium has more audio burning options as well as Blu-ray and HD video conversion capabilities."]},"id":"c2989279-454a-4f96-ad31-1264d2e7d272","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Copy"},"id":"4fa66ad6-abf3-4817-be28-52ed15182d33","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Roxio Popcorn is an excellent resource to copy and export non-copyrighted movie DVDs. For all the home movies and projects, the Mac DVD burning software program will help you easily and quickly burn copies of DVDs and export them to mobile devices, such as an iPhone or PSP.","Unlike the more advanced Roxio product, Titanium Toast 11, Popcorn is not able to import, edit or copy music files. The Roxio Popcorn product is used almost solely for burning DVDs."]},"id":"2b71c458-cc82-461f-a96c-6141abf98bcd","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Output"},"id":"786d4fc3-0b09-4347-a880-dff09606d38e","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The Mac DVD burning software has an assortment of features on top of burning DVDs. There are options to directly publish material to YouTube or Facebook. There are also functions to convert video file types. The program supports Flash and QuickTime file formats. The application can also copy data DVDs for fast and easy storage."]},"id":"76ce02aa-85f4-4816-84e6-1a37c9609dd8","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Customization"},"id":"68e7bd1a-e858-42fb-b46d-4212ff96db40","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Roxio Popcorn can burn non-copyrighted DVDs. The application has DVD compression features from DVD-9 to DVD-5. The Mac DVD burning software will burn DVD-R(W) and DVD+R(W) discs. You can burn data discs with this Mac DVD burning software, but there are no audio support options."]},"id":"b914cddd-f790-44f9-b225-3b8f82f7d8ba","type":"text"},{"data":